rows.label: xs33550100_MSG0020
rows.name: Me? Oh, perfectly fine, as you can see.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33550100_MSG0030
rows.name:
I adjudged that wandering alone was inexpedient,
and so decided to stay on watch right here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33550100_MSG0040
rows.name:
But, now that you are here,
there is nothing else left to wait for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33550100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Let us liberate Al and the Ares,
and end this once and for all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33550100_MSG0060
rows.name:
We have suffered enough loss.
We will be the ones to survive this.[ST:wait ]
